{"tid":1736744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動唔可以停","createTime":"2019-11-18T19:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T00:33:45.000Z","uid":15265,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3503f72253539c9d751481ff1b5883fd50c4705d","tid":1736744,"uid":15265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:36:33.000Z","msg":"Poly事件完左之後 我地慘敗之餘其實班狗都係慘勝 <br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好唔記得經濟先係香港春袋 <br />\n<br />\n黎明行動絕對唔可以停 <br />\n<br />\n一來和理非都可以做塞鐡同快閃RB呢啲相對安全嘅活動 我知冇可能全世界轉勇武 但至少比勇武們有少少休息空間 分擔下勇武壓力之餘加重班狗同政府嘅壓力<br />\n<br />\n二來班狗搞撚左咁耐 都比大部分人走甩左 一定又累 士氣又低 此消彼長  呢兩日想幫手又唔知做咩嘅和理非們真係冇理由唔出 務求要磨撚死班仆街冚家剷 唔撚好比佢停"},{"pid":"884c39b225d2e2ad1a1a0741b08a68fdf72cc14b","tid":1736744,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:38:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動"},{"pid":"97d37444f1e2c27a62fbc4f84032da92e54bfc7f","tid":1736744,"uid":233410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:39:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09c412ce6dfddcbf3d710d994e163910d6df7c3d","tid":1736744,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:40:02.000Z","msg":"瞓唔着嘅，不如入嚟睇下<br />\n<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82dbd91f27578be730ad033629e5ad859eed0e9c","tid":1736744,"uid":318612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:41:24.000Z","msg":"Sorry借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家成日都話手足唔係condom,<br />\n咁我地聽朝一齊去支持佢地</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHmpHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHmpHa.jpg&h=8a668bc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6683459bdc21b3286d60d15a3e4e40878f9d8ee","tid":1736744,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:44:05.000Z","msg":"幫推同借個位<br />\n建議《香城》官方新增新職業 &mdash;&mdash; 燒炭師<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731874</a>"},{"pid":"c466bb17d4528c89a48710fa278f3ae0d078ef6f","tid":1736744,"uid":15265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:48:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">調景嶺 金鐘 九龍塘 呢三個站絕對係兵家必爭之地 一收皮黨鐵就廢左一半 咩魔法都千祈唔好放呢三個站 我好撚想返工</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b42bf7ec59caaf3da6513f38e2732a1ac98ff6","tid":1736744,"uid":301507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:50:06.000Z","msg":"吓你冇嘢化，假到咁。"},{"pid":"2b0018102584e2ddfd3996797d80ecba0e1da3b3","tid":1736744,"uid":15265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:04:35.000Z","msg":"手足們唔可以灰<br />\n<br />\n勝敗為兵家常事，何況雙方嘅武力完全係唔撚對等 正面打頂到兩日 仲號召到咁多手足救人 表現絕對係超班 所以雖然我地今日兵敗如山倒 但殘存絕對有路<br />\n<br />\n想煲底相認就唔可以放棄<br />\n<br />\nPoly手足有錯 我認 但屌完 鬧完 檢討完 大家依然都係手足 佢地就算策略上有錯 但佢地寧死不屈嘅氣魄同毅力 正正係大家都要學習嘅嘢 所以我地絕對冇任何本錢割任何同路人 同行嘅人要互補長短 互相學習 好撚老土 但絕對係真理 屌撚完之後都要諗一諗 你有冇佢地咁撚勁 頂住差唔多全港警力足足兩日嘅大包圍式攻防戰？ <br />\n<br />\n所以反省係要 但唔撚好火氣上頭就分化 真係分化左 大家就等入集中營<br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b3856e97c39befe302fd9a929ec6e71c9ad0f8","tid":1736744,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:14:11.000Z","msg":"休一日先如何 苦戰左咁多人日"},{"pid":"c564ecedeec789acad3483709b1f5bbc52088740","tid":1736744,"uid":258923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tf9Hamd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTf9Hamd.jpg&h=e7aca61e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e8a2baf971a5f37b8153a68cb6cb21ca0b746cf","tid":1736744,"uid":15265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:27:55.000Z","msg":"細力一推"},{"pid":"afae0069d53d1230abb9870acbabfdbe070d0de8","tid":1736744,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:28:51.000Z","msg":"休啦"},{"pid":"6dcaf974055639773475a9fad6e4383006f1f7e6","tid":1736744,"uid":231015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4b3a02ceb264839220cf357d173002be8396b84a","tid":1736744,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"一至五搞好有效 俾六日影響大好那多"},{"pid":"3091f7bef699adf251b09a75475d4d9dae63bfb9","tid":1736744,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T20:30:29.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"870e144299795e4254680ff4b3ca6eaad71772a6","tid":1736744,"uid":159166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3503f72253539c9d751481ff1b5883fd50c4705d","tid":1736744,"uid":15265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T19:36:33.000Z","msg":"Poly事件完左之後 我地慘敗之餘其實班狗都係慘勝 <br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好唔記得經濟先係香港春袋 <br />\n<br />\n黎明行動絕對唔可以停 <br />\n<br />\n一來和理非都可以做塞鐡同快閃RB呢啲相對安全嘅活動 我知冇可能全世界轉勇武 但至少比勇武們有少少休息空間 分擔下勇武壓力之餘加重班狗同政府嘅壓力<br />\n<br />\n二來班狗搞撚左咁耐 都比大部分人走甩左 一定又累 士氣又低 此消彼長  呢兩日